  <h1>📚 The Art of Collection Curation: Building Your Personal Meme Library</h1>
  
  <section class="hero-section">
    <p class="tagline">Master the strategies that transform casual browsing into purposeful curation</p>
    <p class="meta"><strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 14, 2026 | <strong>Reading Time:</strong> 12 minutes | <strong>By:</strong> Meme Explorer Editorial Team</p>
